Step 1 - Make sure vivado is in your PATH. You can check by:
    vivado -version
    xsim -help

Step 2 — Compile SystemVerilog Files
    xvlog -sv design.sv tb.sv

Step 3 — Elaborate Your Testbench
    xelab tb -s tb_sim

Step 4 — Run Simulation and View Waveforms
    xsim tb_sim -gui

Step 5 — Optional: Dump Waveforms Automatically

    initial begin
        $dumpfile("wave.wdb");
        $dumpvars(0, tb); // dump all signals in tb
    end

Step 6 — Quick Run Without GUI (Optional)
    xsim tb_sim -runall